| Net trading & investment income | 410 | 372 | -9.3% |
| Other operating income | 188 | 201 | +6.9% |
| Total operating income | 6,948 | 7,258 | +4.5% |
| Operating expenses | (1,720) | (1,749) | +1.7% |
| Net impairment losses | (640) | (498) | -22.2% |
| Profit before tax | 4,588 | 5,011 | +9.2% |
| Income tax expense | (740) | (891) | +20.4% |
| Net profit for the period | 3,848 | 4,120 | +7.1% |

metric: Total Operating Income | value: 7258 | unit: QAR millions
metric: Net Profit for the Period | value: 4120 | unit: QAR millions

revenue: Net interest income | value: 5480 | unit: QAR millions | driver: margin expansion + 2.8% loan growth | period: Q2 2026
revenue: Net fee & commission income | value: 1205 | unit: QAR millions | driver: trade finance and card fees | period: Q2 2026
cost-of-risk: Annualised provisioning charge | value: 0.41 | unit: % of gross loans | trend: down | period: Q2 2026

break:

